# corndogs/Dockerfile builds from the repo root (to include clients/corndogs). Keep the
# build context lean: drop VCS metadata and every language's build artifacts. In CI the
# tree is a fresh clone (no artifacts), but this keeps local `docker build .` fast too.
.git
corndogs/main
**/node_modules
**/target
**/dist
**/.dart_tool
**/_build
**/build
**/bin
**/obj
**/.gradle
**/__pycache__
**/*.egg-info
**/pubspec.lock
